Package com.agilent.labs.hyperedge.event

Interfaces and support classes that define HyperEdge event management.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
ChangeListener Interface for determining how a HyperEdge object has changed.
DeleteListener Interface for retrieving information on the destruction of a HyperEdge.
NewObjectListener Interface for retrieving information on the creation of a new HyperEdge object.
 

Class Summary
EventNote Houses information about an event notification.
EventNote.SubType Specifies the sub-type of this type of event notification.
EventNote.Type Specifies the types of Event Notification objects.
